	<div class="row" id="help-div" style="display:none;">
		<li class="list-group-item">
		<p>
		<h4>Editor interaction</h4>
		<pre>Click         : Select a point</pre>
		<pre>Ctrl - click  : Select a vertex and all linked vertices</pre>
		<pre>Drag          : move a vertex (or selected vertices) around, or do a group selection if you didn't click on a vertex</pre>
		<pre>Ctrl - drag   : Move around the map</pre>
		<pre>Shift - click : Create a new vertex, or link the currently selected vertex with the one you clicked on </pre>


		<br>
		<h4>Keyboard commands</h4>
		<pre>Ctrl - c      : Copy the current selection</pre>
		<pre>Ctrl - v      : Paste the last copied selection</pre>
		<pre>Del           : Delete selection </pre>
		<pre>m             : Toggle the menu </pre>

		<br>
		<h4>Other</h4>
		<pre>Mousewheel    : Zoom in and out</pre>
		</p>
